@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Concept Car";
}

@section Styles {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/pages/concept-car.css" asp-append-version="true" />
}

<!-- 1. HERO: car2.jpg -->
<section class="cc-hero">
  <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/car2.jpg" alt="JOY Concept Car">
  <div class="cc-hero-overlay"></div>
</section>

<!-- 2. KEYWORDS INTRO -->
<section class="cc-keywords fade-in">
  <h3>JOY: KEYWORDS OF THE DESIGN CONCEPT ARE...</h3>
  <p>BAIC brand JOY concept car interprets the design concept of CAPITAL BEAUTY.<br>It will bring users a quiet sense of satisfaction and practical comfort.<br>The design of "confident, warm and Oriental charm" is the beautiful vision of the<br>BAIC brand for future travel.</p>
</section>

<!-- 3. LOGO -->
<section class="cc-logo fade-in">
  <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/logo.png" alt="BAIC Logo">
</section>

<!-- 4. CAR BG -->
<section class="cc-fullimg fade-in">
  <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/carbg.jpg" alt="JOY Concept Car">
</section>

<!-- 5. ELEMENTS DESCRIPTION -->
<section class="cc-elements fade-in">
  <p>We extracted the basic elements from the humanistic characteristics and urban<br>architecture of the East, and continued to study, aiming at the linear curvature design<br>and the processing of chamfer, the basic pattern was formed, with order and<br>temperature.</p>
</section>

<!-- 6. THE BALANCED NUMBER: FIVE -->
<section class="cc-five fade-in">
  <h4>The balanced number: Five</h4>
  <div class="cc-five-icons">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image9.png" alt="five">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image9.png" alt="five">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image9.png" alt="five">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image9.png" alt="five">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image9.png" alt="five">
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 7. JOYFUL: 3 cards (label on top, car below) -->
<section class="cc-joyful fade-in">
  <div class="cc-joy-card">
    <div class="cc-joy-label"><span>Joyful</span><h4>Off-road performance</h4></div>
    <div class="cc-joy-car">
      <img class="car-light" src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/car_light1.png" alt="">
      <img class="shadow-car" src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/shadow_car1.png" alt="Off-road">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cc-joy-card">
    <div class="cc-joy-label"><span>Joyful</span><h4>Outdoor experience</h4></div>
    <div class="cc-joy-car">
      <img class="car-light" src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/car_light3.png" alt="">
      <img class="shadow-car" src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/shadow_car2.png" alt="Outdoor">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cc-joy-card">
    <div class="cc-joy-label"><span>Joyful</span><h4>Stylish journey</h4></div>
    <div class="cc-joy-car">
      <img class="car-light" src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/car_light2.png" alt="">
      <img class="shadow-car" src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/shadow_car3.png" alt="Stylish">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 8. FIVE-HOLE ELEMENT TEXT -->
<section class="cc-fivehole fade-in">
  <p>Regarding the design of the front face, we start from the basic graphics and combine the balanced and<br>stable number "five" to form a highly identifiable "five-hole element" design, representing the integrity of<br>the Eastern spirit. Combined with the requirements of different models of the BAIC brand, the five<br>elements of differentiation are formed to strengthen the visual identity of the BAIC brand.</p>
</section>

<!-- 9. FRONT FACE IMAGE -->
<section class="cc-fullimg fade-in">
  <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image10.jpg" alt="Five-hole element">
</section>

<!-- 10. CAR LINE / DIMENSIONS -->
<section class="cc-dims fade-in">
  <div class="cc-dims-img">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/car_line.png" alt="Car line dimensions">
  </div>
  <div class="cc-dims-arrows">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/left_arrow.png" alt="←">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/right_arrow.png" alt="→">
  </div>
  <p>The "poised" ratio. The JOY concept car is 5013 mm long, 2042 mm wide and has a wheelbase of 3000 mm. Large shaft ratio and low wind resistance profile bring stable posture and spacious interior space to the user.</p>
</section>

<!-- 11. SURFACE / SHADOW DOOR -->
<section class="cc-surface fade-in">
  <div class="cc-surface-imgs">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image11.jpg" alt="Surface design">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/shadow_door.png" alt="Shadow door">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/xian.png" alt="Line detail">
  </div>
  <p>"Leisurely" surface. The simple and pure curved design, combined with the strong wheel arch surface, creates a safe body image, with speed, and cutting sense of the line, reflecting the young fashion, as well as a sense of controlled movement.</p>
</section>

<!-- 12. ORIENTAL & STYLISH + GIF -->
<section class="cc-oriental fade-in">
  <div class="cc-oriental-text">
    <h3>Oriental<br>& stylish</h3>
    <p>The details of the Oriental tide<br>combined with fashion</p>
  </div>
  <div class="cc-oriental-img">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image2.gif" alt="Oriental stylish">
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 13. INTERIOR TEXT + GIF -->
<section class="cc-interior fade-in">
  <div class="cc-interior-text">
    <p>The interior design of the JOY concept car<br>shows the charm of warmth and national<br>tide everywhere.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="cc-interior-img">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image1.gif" alt="Interior design">
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 14. TWO BJ + Scenario-based Design -->
<section class="cc-twobj fade-in">
  <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/two_bj.jpg" alt="Two BJ">
  <div class="cc-twobj-overlay"><h3>Scenario-based Design</h3></div>
</section>

<!-- 15. INTERIOR DETAILS GRID -->
<section class="cc-details fade-in">
  <div class="cc-details-top">
    <div class="dt-main">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image4.jpg" alt="Interior detail">
    </div>
    <div class="dt-text">
      <p>The fashion design expression technique is used to integrate Oriental aesthetic elements into the interior design.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cc-details-grid">
    <div class="cc-detail-card">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image5.jpg" alt="Ripple panel">
      <span>Ripple-design control panel</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cc-detail-card">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image6.jpg" alt="Fu character panel">
      <span>"福"character sound panel</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cc-detail-card">
      <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image7.jpg" alt="Oriental cockpit">
      <span>Oriental style cockpit</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- 16. CLOSING: image8 + text -->
<section class="cc-closing fade-in">
  <div class="cc-closing-img">
    <img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/public/static/topic/2023-capital-beauty-redefined/images/image8.jpg" alt="JOY Future">
  </div>
  <div class="cc-closing-text">
    <p>In the coming<br>years, JOY will<br>inspire the BAIC<br>brand's strong<br>product lineup.<br>We firmly<br>believe that<br>BAIC will bring<br>thousands of<br>families the<br>best trave<br>experience!</p>
  </div>
</section>

@section Scripts {
}
